issue.title: Feature: Edit post

milestone.title: M1 Milestone
milestone.description:
Reviewing the progress made in the TDD Implementation.
 - Feature work completed.
 - Reviewing Issues closed/pending

issue.body:
Feature: Edit Post

1. API call to edit post (Takes postId, versionId, content)
2. Call to postManager to edit post
3. Postmanager retrieves post using postId (handle id not found)
4. Postmanager retrieves version using versionId (handle id not found)
5. If version is in DRAFT state, replace content, if version is in PUBLISHED/ARCHIVED states, create new version in DRAFT state and replace content

milestone.title: M1 Milestone
milestone.description:
Reviewing the progress made in the TDD Implementation.
 - Feature work completed.
 - Reviewing Issues closed/pending

issue.body:
Feature: Edit Post

1. API call to edit post (Takes postId, versionId, content)
2. Call to postManager to edit post
3. Postmanager retrieves post using postId (handle id not found)
4. Postmanager retrieves version using versionId (handle id not found)
5. If version is in DRAFT state, replace content, if version is in PUBLISHED/ARCHIVED states, create new version in DRAFT state and replace content
